	)
	(text "- Choose Crystal(Q),\n  Load Cap(CL), Feed\n  Res(RExt)\n- Estimate Stray Cap(Cs)\n- ~ 3 to 5 pF\n- CL = 2*(C0-Cs)=10pF\n- where C0 is load cap\n\nCrystal Params\n- f0=16MHz, C0=10pF, ESR=80MHz\n\nFeed Resistor\n- RC Low Pass Filter \n	-> Limits Harmonics\n- Limits Drive Level\n	-> Prevents Distortion\n- Rext=10%*(2*pi*f*C)=100Ohms\n- Often times no need\n- Just place 0Ohms Res."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 19.304 126.492 0)
		(effects
